      "role": "user",
      "content": "\"Civil Uprising\" feels a bit heavy, maybe too intense for what's happening? idk. \n\ncan u give me a few more options but specifically focus on the groups that are actually involved? like, if this was a protest about, say, veterans rights or something, how would u phrase it vs this? i want to see the difference in how u'd frame the \"energy\" of the situation depending on the group.",
